 mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">내재 동기</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(intrinsic motivation)</span></strong></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 10.0pt; text-indent: -10.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 10pt; text-indent: -10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">:&nbsp;</span><strong><span data-mce-style=\"color: #000080;\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 128);\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">활동 그 자체를 위해 참여하는 동기</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학습의 경우 공부 그 자체가 가치 있다고 여기기 때문에 공부를 함</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">외재 동기와 내재 동기를 연속선상의 양극단</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">외재 동기가 높으면 내재 동기가 낮고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span d