gn: center; word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">인간으로서 자신의 잠재력을 완전히 발휘하고자 하는 노력을 강조</span></p><div><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\"><br></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table>',7269,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(173,47,'B. 학습동기에 대한 욕구의 영향','2018-03-02 13:02:15','<p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">2)&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\">학습동기에 대한 욕구의 영향</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">동기이론에서 욕구는 특정한 상태나 사물을 얻거나 피하기 위한 내면적 힘 또는 추동</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(1)&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">매슬로우의 욕구위계이론</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">매슬로우는 심리학에서 인본주의 사조의 아버지로 여겨지며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">전인적 인간의 욕구를 반영하는 위계를 발전시킴</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">성장 욕구는 경험이 풍부해지면서 더 많아지는 지적 성취와 심미적 인식에 대한 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">결핍과 성장 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 10.0pt; text-indent: -10.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 10pt; text-indent: -10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">:&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">결핍 욕구는 충족되지 않았을 때 인간으로 하여금 그것을 충족하고자 노력하게 하는 욕구</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">생존</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">안전</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">소속</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자존감 등</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">).&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">결핍 욕구가 모두 충족되지 않으면 성장 욕구로 옮겨 가지 않음</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">성장 욕구는 우리가 지닌 잠재력에 최대한 도달하고 자신실현을 이끌고자 하는 욕구</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">결코 완전히 충족되지 않음</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(2)&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자기결정에 대한 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자기결정은 자신의 환경에 따라 행동하고 환경을 통제하고자 하는 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자기결정이론에서는 인간은 유능성</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자율성</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">관계성 요구를 가진다고 가정함</span></p>',10,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(174,47,'1. 유능성욕구','2018-03-02 13:02:38','<p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">유능성은 효과적으로 기능하는 능력</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">유능성 욕구는 왜 도전적이고 호기심을 유발하는 활동이 내재적으로 동기 부여하는지 설명하는데 도움을 줌</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">유능성 욕구는 화이트</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(White)</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">의 환경에 대한 지배욕구와 유사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">유능성 욕구는 특정 영역에 정통하거나 잘 해내고자 하는 욕구를 강조하는 성취동기이론의 설명과 일치</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생들이 자신의 유능성을 지각할 수 있는 가장 중요한 요소는 학생들의 지식과 기술이 증가하고 있다는 증거를 보여주는 것</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">#학생의 유능성에 영향을 미치는 교사의 행동</span></p><table data-mce-style=\"border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; mso-table-overlap: never; border: none;\" class=\"mce-item-table\" style=\"border: none; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 88.08pt; height: 44.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; background: #cacaca; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 88.08pt; height: 44.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; background: rgb(202, 202, 202);\"><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\">교사의 귀인방식</span></p></td><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 331.46pt; height: 44.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 331.46pt; height: 44.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt;\"><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교사의 귀인방식은 교사가 학생의 수행 원인을 어디에 두는 가의 문제</span></p><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생의 능력 부족에 원인을 두지 말고 노력 부족에 원인을 두는 것이 학생의 수행 의지를 강화함</span></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 88.08pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; background: #cacaca; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 88.08pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; background: rgb(202, 202, 202);\"><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\">칭찬과 비판</span></p></td><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 331.46pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 331.46pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt;\"><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">부적절한 칭찬은 오히려 학습동기를 손상시킬 수 있으며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">반대로 시의적절한 비판은 학습동기를 높임</span></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 88.08pt; height: 60.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; background: #cacaca; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 88.08pt; height: 60.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; background: rgb(202, 202, 202);\"><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\">감정적 반응</span></p></td><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 331.46pt; height: 60.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 331.46pt; height: 60.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt;\"><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학습자의 성공과 실패에 대한 교사의 감정적 반응 역시 영향을 미침</span></p><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학습자가 실패했을 때 불쾌감을 표현하는 교사는 학생이 노력을 더 하면 능력을 갖출 수 있다고 믿는 것으로 보이며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">동정을 표하는 교사는 학생이 유능해질 만한 능력이 별로 없다고 믿는 것으로 보임</span></p></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 88.08pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; background: #cacaca; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 88.08pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; background: rgb(202, 202, 202);\"><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"text-align: center; word-break: keep-all;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; font-weight: bold;\">도움의 제공</span></p></td><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 331.46pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 331.46pt; height: 28.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt;\"><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생이 도움을 요청하지 않은 상태에서 교사가 도움을 주는 것 역시 문제가 되고 유능감의 감소를 야기할 수 있음</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>',10,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(175,47,'2. 자율성 욕구','2018-03-02 13:02:51','<p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">⓶&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자율성 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자율성 욕구는 독립성에 대한 욕구이며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">필요할 때 환경을 바꿀 수 있는 능력으로서 자기결정이론에 의해 설명된 인간의 두 번째 선천적 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자율성은 통제소재</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(Rotter),&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">개인적 인과유형</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(deCharms)</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">과 같은 주제와 유사</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교사가 학생들의 자율성에 대한 지각을 높이기 위해 선택할 수 있는 가장 분명한 방법은 학생들에게 선택할 수 있는 기회를 제공하는 것</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\">&nbsp;</p><table data-mce-style=\"border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; mso-table-overlap: never; border: none;\" class=\"mce-item-table\" style=\"border: none; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"middle\" data-mce-style=\"width: 419.54pt; height: 92.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.10pt 1.41pt 5.10pt; background: #dddddd; border: solid #000000 0.28pt;\" style=\"border: 0.28pt solid rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 419.54pt; height: 92.82pt; padding: 1.41pt 5.1pt; background: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생들에게 교실의 규칙과 절차를 만드는 과정에 의견을 제시하도록 한다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생들에게 자신의 학습목표를 설정하고 모니터하도록 격려한다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교실활동에서 학생 참여가 높은 수준으로 이루어지게 한다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">성취에 대해서 노력과 전략 사용의 효과를 강조하고 능력의 영향을 덜 강조하도록 한다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">평가 시 피드백을 제공하고 학습이 향상되는 것에 초점을 둔다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>',10,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(176,47,'3. 관계성 욕구','2018-03-02 13:03:08','<p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">⓷&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">관계성 욕구</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">관계성은 사회환경 속에서 다른 사람들과 연관되어 있다는 느낌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">사랑과 존경받을 가치가 있다는 느낌</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">관계성 욕구는 학생들에게 강한 인정 욕구</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">즉 다른 사람들에 의해 수용되고 긍정적으로 평가받고자 하는 욕구로 발전하는 결과를 야기할 수 있음</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">교사들은 학생들에게 무조건적인 긍정적 존중을 전달하고 학생과 학습에 대해 진정한 헌신을 함으로써 학생들의 관계성 욕구와 인정 욕구를 충족시키는 데 도움을 줄 수 있음</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생들은 교사가 자신을 좋아하고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">이해하고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">공감해 준다고 믿을 때 행동적</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">·</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">인지적</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">·</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">정서적 측면에서 수업활동에 더 열심히 참여</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자기결정에서 평가의 역할</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 10.0pt; text-indent: -10.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 10pt; text-indent: -10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">:&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">평가가 자신을 처벌하기 위해서나 통제하기 위한 수단이라고 여긴다면 평가는 학생의 내재 동기를 손상시키는 반면</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">평가가 자신의 능력이 증진한다는 정보를 제공한다고 여긴다면 학생의 내재 동기는 향상될 수 있음</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.&nbsp;</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학습과 유능감 증진을 강조하는 환경을 조성하는 것이 학생성취를 평가하는 목표가 되어야 함</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자기결정성을 높이기 위해 평가를 사용하는 방법</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">학생들에게 분명한 기대를 제공하고 이러한 기대와 일치하도록 평가를 조정하라</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" data-mce-style=\"margin-left: 5.0pt; text-indent: -5.0pt; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\" style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: 5pt; text-indent: -5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\">*</span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕;\" style=\"font-family: 함초롬바탕;\">자주</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" data-mce-style=\"mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-text-raise: